OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Mary Holley
OL,5,FMary Holley, Age 100, Royal Navy spouse
OL,7,FInterviewed 15 November 2023
OL,9,FWorking in a firm helping the war
OL,10,Feffort, Mary Holley met her late
OL,11,Fhusband Roy before he joined the Royal
OL,12,FNavy and was sent to the Far East with
OL,13,Fthe battleship HMS Frobisher.
OL,15,FThey married two months before D-Day
OL,16,Fwhen he came home on leave.
