OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Mary Holley
OL,5,FShe said: "D-Day was coming up. They
OL,6,Fhad seven days and that was that. He
OL,7,Fcame home on Monday and we married on
OL,8,FWednesday and then he went back to his
OL,9,Fship on the second Monday."
OL,11,FMrs Holley, like others, suspected
OL,12,Fsome military operation was about to
OL,13,Fhappen and that her new husband's ship
OL,14,Fhad returned.
OL,16,F"Before D-Day - months before - the
OL,17,Fwhole of the South coast was cordoned
OL,18,Foff," she said.
