OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Mary Holley
OL,5,F"And they thought she was going to
OL,6,Fsink so the order was given that they
OL,7,Fshould abandon ship. With Roy you only
OL,8,Fheard the funny stories. He was below
OL,9,Fsomewhere and had to make his way up
OL,10,Fto deck. He picked up someone's
OL,11,Fbreakfast left on someone's plate so
OL,12,Fhe went into the sea carrying
OL,13,Fsomeone's breakfast.
OL,15,F"I don't know how long they were in
OL,16,Fthe sea. But the one thing he did say
OL,17,Fabout it was about the oily water they
OL,18,Fswallowed. So the ship didn't sink.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
