OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Mary Holley
OL,5,F"And they were considered safer on
OL,6,Fboard than in the sea. I don't know
OL,7,Fwhat they did in the sea because if a
OL,8,Fship was going down you got away from
OL,9,Fit because you didn't want to be
OL,10,Fsucked in with all the water. So they
OL,11,Fmust have been some way away from the
OL,12,Fship.
OL,14,F"They were picked up again and climbed
OL,15,Fback on board and she made her way
OL,16,Fback to her station.
