OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Mary Holley
OL,5,F"I was anxious a bit but not worried.
OL,6,FIt was probably fool's whatever but
OL,7,Fnothing was going to happen to
OL,8,FRoyston. He was coming home. That was
OL,9,Fthat.
OL,11,F"That was all that could keep you
OL,12,Fgoing really."
OL,14,FFollowing a happy marriage, Roy died
OL,15,Fin 2014.
OL,17,FMrs Holley is now a resident with
OL,18,FRoyal Star & Garter, a charity
OL,19,Fproviding care to veterans and their
OL,20,Fpartners living with disability.
